WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.259 --> 00:00:03.787
OALC has two fundamental roles.

2
00:00:03.787 --> 00:00:06.418
First, it has an operational role to provide

3
00:00:06.418 --> 00:00:09.283
acquisition, logistics, construction,

4
00:00:09.283 --> 00:00:11.131
and leasing support to the Department's

5
00:00:11.131 --> 00:00:13.554
administrations and staff offices

6
00:00:13.554 --> 00:00:15.869
so they can accomplish their missions.

7
00:00:15.869 --> 00:00:18.417
Second, it has oversight responsibility

8
00:00:18.417 --> 00:00:20.554
on behalf of the Secretary to ensure

9
00:00:20.554 --> 00:00:23.186
VA complies with laws, policies,

10
00:00:23.186 --> 00:00:26.287
and directions from executive branch partners,

11
00:00:26.287 --> 00:00:28.684
such as the Office of Management and Budget,

12
00:00:28.684 --> 00:00:32.218
Department of Treasury, General Services Administration,

13
00:00:32.218 --> 00:00:35.265
Government Accountability Office, and Congress.

